data.description: This well-crafted open flrpln invites connectivity w/family and friends.The stairs are tucked away from out of sight & the study has lrg windows for nice lighting. The cvrd patio comes w/a fireplace & the gm rm is pre-wired for surround sound for those sporting events or movies. The wood-looking ceramic tile in the main areas brings a contemporary elegance while upgrades such as the trash can pull out in the kitchen cabinets and floor plugs in the fm rm offer convenient functionality. Ready in September!
